VISUALIZER
------------------------------

To run visualizer:
./visualizer megazord.gamelog


  Key  |  Function
       |
   P   | Pause/Play
   R   | Rewind
   +   | Increase Speed
   -   | Decrease Speed
   >   | Go ahead one frame
   <   | Go back one frame
   E   | Go to last frame
   S   | Go to first frame
 Left  | Move Cursor Left
 Right | Move Cursor Right
  Up   | Move Cursor Up
 Down  | Move Cursor Down


If for any reason the visualizer does not exit cleanly and the terminal is bugged, type "reset" into your bash prompt and hit enter.
Note: This works even if you cannot see the text.


